---
title: Creamy Chickpea Salad Sandwiches with Lemony Spinach & Potato Wedges
description: This week, the humble chickpea is transformed into a bold and hearty vegetarian meal sure to evoke deli sandwich dreams. Mashed chickpeas are combined with a creamy, rich dressing, citrusy dill, and scallions for a flavorful filling that’s slathered onto toasted sourdough with a heap of lemony spinach. Oh, and there are crispy potato wedges too for a one-two punch of pure dining pleasure.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chickpea-salad-sandwiches-0487d498.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-chickpea-salad-sandwiches-63333380bb98a9007e0c810a-7203841b.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 1060 kcal
  fat: 49 g
  saturated fat: 11 g
  carbohydrates: 134 g
  sugar: 12 g
  protein: 22 g
